code: import axios from'axios';import{URL}from'../constants/urls';import{KEY}from'../constants/keys';const getCity=async city=>{try{const response=await axios.get(`${URL.WEATHER}${city}${URL.UNITS}${URL.APPID}${KEY.API}`);return response.data;}catch(error){console.log(error);}};export default{getCity};
